name: Mariana Lucas
description: I seek a monogamous, passionate, romantic man wants to spend his life with one soul mate, build a house and make a home and family together. I’m looking for a man who is not ashamed of being a man, but knows that doesn’t mean being a barbarian. If you know what love is and are emotionally available, write to me.and i want you to know that distance should not be a barrier..do have a nice time
